Watermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:633,&quot;width&quot;:950,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:704,&quot;bytes&quot;:166429,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3986bcc1-d2cd-455a-b039-b0927375952c_950x633.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3986bcc1-d2cd-455a-b039-b0927375952c_950x633.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3986bcc1-d2cd-455a-b039-b0927375952c_950x633.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3986bcc1-d2cd-455a-b039-b0927375952c_950x633.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">照片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@krakenimages?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">krakenimages</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/man-in-white-dress-shirt-sitting-beside-woman-in-black-long-sleeve-shirt-376KN_ISplE?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄</figcaption></figure></div><p>我和人工智能领域的很多人交往过，如果他们确信一件事，那就是他们正在开发的技术将使很多人失业。也许不是所有人——他们为此争论不休——但肯定有<em>很多</em>人。</p><p>他们有这样的想法是可以理解的；毕竟，这几乎就是他们发明东西的方式。他们想“好吧，人们愿意花钱为他们做什么样的事情？”，然后他们试图找出如何让人工智能做到这一点。由于这些任务几乎都是人类当前所做的事情，这意味着人工智能工程师、创始人和风险投资家几乎总是致力于自动化人类劳动。因此，如果我们继续这样做，一遍又一遍，最终很多人将无事可做，这并不夸张。</p><p>人们很自然地认为这种活动会压低工资。直观地说，如果人类有报酬去做一系列事情，而其中一些事情不断被自动化，那么人类劳动力将被挤进越来越少的任务中。基本上，这个想法是这样的： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg" width="1456" height="633" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a785391f-ab3f-4d26-b9d0-1abb98743184_1512x657.jpeg&quot;,&