sizes="100vw"></picture><div></div></div></figure></div><p> 《纪事报》报道了关于这次选举意义的各种观点，作为我们称之为“旧金山政治”的狂热梦想的长期观察者和参与者，我认为我可以通过以下方式帮助您理解这一切：<br><br> <strong>— 我会告诉你到底发生了什么</strong></p><p><strong>— 我会告诉你人们对于这件事发生的原因有不同的理论，包括我的！</strong></p><p> <strong>— 在我的下一篇文章中，我将解释我认为接下来会发生什么</strong></p><h4><strong><br>那么究竟发生了什么？</strong> </h4><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_360x270.png" width="360" height="270" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/37c116b3-e1db-461e-9888-f03c4d61a52d_3