"https://www.orchidhealth.com/">Orchid</a>的初创公司，从事 IVF 基因筛查，因此她谈论了很多与生育和生育相关的话题。斯蒂芬想制作一集关于科技世界中的约会和浪漫的剧集，但我不知何故最终被卷入其中。这不是我通常谈论的话题，但我想我在其中添加了一些有趣的观点。由于技术错误，我们没有视频，但音频非常有趣： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a9e32046b143a13439b7bb9cd&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Dating, gendered timelines, and masculine versus feminine energy with Noah Smith and Steph Sher&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noor Siddiqui&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/6UY53r1FMgHBejNOF8cvRT&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/6UY53r1FMgHBejNOF8cvRT" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这是 <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/conceivable-with-noor/id1721905069?i=1000647549158">苹果播客</a>上的内容。</p><p>我还和 Erik Torenberg 一起制作了两集 Econ 102。这是关于建立多种族社会的一篇文章。它的灵感来自于谷歌的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/this-is-not-a-good-way-to-fight-racism">双子座惨败</a>，但我们最终甚至没有谈论这个，而只是谈论民族主义和归属感等等。 </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8a9fcbd27685efd58d05819bad&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Building a Multi Racial Society&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/0ltLXBqGmgBCs7z6PtrNn1&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/0ltLXBqGmgBCs7z6PtrNn1" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>这里是<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/no/podcast/building-a-multi-racial-society/id1696419056?i=1000647500481">Apple 播客</a>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?