age/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg" width="642" height="533.9475409836066" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:761,&quot;width&quot;:915,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:642,&quot;bytes&quot;:169617,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa957feb3-55e2-46bf-925d-ddffbf749864_915x761.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>许多人跳到斯特凡尼克身上回答“当然不是”。毕竟，四年前我们正处于新冠大流行的开始阶段。 2020 年将因大规模失业、封锁、骚乱、犯罪率飙升以及数百万人死于疾病而永远被人们铭记。这并不有趣。</p><p>但仅仅给出答案并宣布胜利就太容易了。人们凭直觉就知道，2020 年的大部分恐怖事件并不是特朗普造成的。他们倾向于将 2020 年视为特朗普和拜登总统任期之间的过渡期。因此，当他们思考“你的情况更好了吗？”这个问题时，他们会考虑<em>与 2019 年相比</em>，自己的情况是否更好——大流行前一年，经济强劲，就业率高，通胀率高。低等。</p><p>事实是，即使与 2019 年相比，大多数美国人的状况也有所改善——至少从纯粹的经济意义上来说是这样。</p><p>我的意思是，只要看看美国人的消费量就知道了。这是真实的个人消费支出——“真实”意味着“根据通货膨胀调整”： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04e83d41-1906-4724-a6e3-5fa66ed11db0_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04e83d41-1906-4724-a6e3-5fa66ed11db0_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaw